{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>问题描述：</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span> &nbsp;这是最近遇到的一个关于</span><span><a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=Anaconda&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">Anaconda</a></span><span>的小问题。</span><span> &nbsp;用</span><span><a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=conda&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">conda</a></span><span>创建一个名为 </span><span>pytorch</span><span> 的环境想学习pytorch，安装完一切之后在 jupyter 中找不到 pytorch 这个</span><span>虚拟环境</span><span>，与之相关的库也都无法调用</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>解决方法：</span>","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>实际上是由于在</span><span><a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">虚拟环境</a></span><span>下缺少kernel.json文件，首先安装ipykernel，在Prompt中切换到 </span><span>tf</span><span> 环境输入：</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"code","data":{"lang":"","lines":["<span class=\"be-code__attribute\">conda</span> install ipykernel"]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>再将环境写入notebook的kernel中</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"code","data":{"lang":"","lines":["python -m ipykernel install <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--user</span> <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--name</span> pytorch <span class=\"be-code__attr\">--display-name</span> \"Python (pytorch )\"","//自己将pytorch 替换为你的环境"]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>这样就添加完成了！</span><span>输入 </span><span><a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=jupyter&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">jupyter</a></span><span> notebook 进入查看：</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"url":"https://rqh3nmk4yk3.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=MGQ1ZTA1ZDJhMTJiZTQyOWQ4NTk0NDcxNDczMTk5YjJfNW1qWXRHTTFCOEJUWmFIOG9iYTNWcXNqN0lUbHg5ZWhfVG9rZW46V2h1cmJZejZGb3ltblp4SFpUcmNNSU1P